      "content": "it's just so hard to imagine anything \"new\" when everything feels so dead already. when you say \"find a way to make it stop\" or \"escape the pain\"... it sounds like you're saying i don't have to keep fighting this. like maybe there's actually a way to just... stop. is that even a valid thing to want? to just be done with it all?",
